fields.name: ELLY WIDE LEG JUMPSUIT - SLATE BLUE
fields.description: The Elly Jumpsuit in slate blue is our classic silhouette curated to make an elegant statement. A one - shoulder jumpsuit with an asymmetric neckline and simple square cut out to elevate and highlight your form.A fitted bodice flows seamlessly into high - waisted flattering wide leg palazzo trousers to balance the whole look. Completed with a concealed side zip for seamless perfect fit.

fields.name: PARKER JUMPSUIT - LILAC
fields.description: Your go-to event favourite is the Parker Jumpsuit in an all-new lilac. Featuring a one-shoulder asymmetric neckline personifies an effortless finesse. Fitted at the waist, this wide-leg jumpsuit's distinctive panel overlay makes this style a visually versatile combination of maxi dress meets jumpsuit. The perfect addition to your occasion wardrobe.

fields.name: CANICE ONE SHOULDER MINI DRESS
fields.description: This is a smooth decaf Indonesian coffee with a medium strength profile. Some of the flavours that might come through are Chocolate Brownie and Cherry.

fields.name: CINDY WRAP DRESS
fields.description: Introducing the Cindy wrap dress. The perfect day-to-night statement dress with a flattering feminine fit. Peplum frill sleeves and trim add drama to the silhouette, finished off with a tie waist at the back. A perfectly chic addition to your wardrobe.

fields.name: VALEN ONE SHOULDER MINI DRESS
fields.description: The statement mini of your dreams? The Valen fitted black mini dress is a monochrome fantasy. This one-shoulder piece delicately highlights your figure with understated simplicity. Contrasted with an opulent pleated black and white extended sleeve, with a split on the inner seam, adds movement, fluidity, and drama to your look. Finished with an invisible centre back seam zip. The mini you have been waiting for has arrived.

fields.name: CANDICE ONE SHOULDER MINI DRESS
fields.description: The Candice mini dress in red features a double shoulder strap and cut-out back detail. One-shoulder style dress with asymmetric hemline and side split. Fitted mini dress fully lined in a soft-touch lining. Concealed zip fastening to the side.

fields.name: MACRAME BACKBACK
fields.description: Ditch the bumbag this festival season and opt for this backpack. Designed with a macrame finish, this bag features a foldover flap and adjustable straps to keep your festival essentials safe and secure.

fields.name: NATALIE SUEDETTE ENVELOPE CLUCH BAG BLUE
fields.description: Sleek and sophisticated, our Natalie clutch makes an elegant option for evenings out. It has a soft suedette outer with a magnetic press stud fastening and an optional chain strap.

fields.name: MESSENGER BAG
fields.description: Part of our vegan collection, registered with The Vegan Society. This faux leather number makes the perfect everyday bag. It fastens with a zip at the top and has an adjustable strap to wear across your body.To help organise your items, there 's both an internal and external zip pocket.

fields.name: HEART PRINT WASHBAG
fields.description: Spread the love with this heart print washbag. Just throw in your favourite beauty bits and you'll be feeling lovely wherever you go.

fields.name: ALIVIA TOTE BAG BLACK
fields.description: A clean, simplistic style that's suitable for both office meetings and day trips into town, Alivia will complement any of your outfits with ease. She's designed in sturdy faux leather with long straps to style over the shoulder, whilst the interior secures with a zip fastening and magnetic snap closure to ensure your possessions are safe on your ventures.
